nodes.text: BT-9093 was a stormtrooper of the First Order. Present during the First Order's blockade of Kashyyyk, BT-9093 and another stormtrooper were ordered to locate SN-1208, who had failed to report in after being incapacitated by the Wookiee Chewbacca. The two stormtroopers encountered the porg Terbus, who led them into a trap set up by Chewbacca.
